cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper focuses on evaluating long-term tracking algorithms, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed evaluation strategies also involve analyzing the reliability and recovery of the trackers, which are important aspects of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves visual inference, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
